        Product Info for Burris AR-PEPR Tactical Riflescope Rings with Mount


If you struggle to choose between your favorite full-sized riflescopes, then the Burris AR-PEPR Tactical Riflescope Rings with Mount is the mount for you. Able to mount almost any riflescope, this Riflescope Mount from Burris easily attaches on any AR with Picatinny rail uppers. Featuring two inches of forward scope positioning, the Burris AR-PEPR Tactical Riflescope Rings with Picatinny Mount helps achieve a full field overview and excellent eye relief from harsh recoil. When you need to fit your largest or longest optics securely to your rifle, the Burris AR-PEPR Riflescope Rings keep your favorite scope precisely where you need it for years to come.
Burris Ring Height Sizing Chart


Specifications for AR-PEPR Tactical with Mount:



Finish:
Matte





Features of Burris AR Matte Black Tactical Mounts:

Proper Eye Position Ready
Single unit ring base
Ring top Picatinny rails
Quick Detach options



Package Contents:

Burris AR-PEPR Mount



Burris AR-PEPR Scope Mount, 30mm 410341
Burris AR-PEPR Scope Mount, 1in 410343
Burris AR-PEPR Scope Mount, 1in - Quick Detach - 410344
Burris AR-PEPR Scope Mount, 30mm - Quick Detach - 410342








