                Burris Eliminator III Riflescopes, Tough, Lightweight, On Sale! — 3 products / 3 models
 — Page 1










Burris Eliminator III riflescopes excel at extreme ranges. Even at ranges over 1,200 yards, the built-in rangefinder and custom trajectory compensation calculate your aiming point in seconds. The controls on Burris Eliminator III scopes make all the magic as easy to master as your bedside alarm clock. Mount your Eliminator III riflescope quickly and easily on Weaver or Picatinny rails because it comes with its own bases -- no rings needed. Since they are are produced by Burris, they also come with precision ground lenses, Hi-Lume multicoating, high-grade optical glass and other Burris features to create riflescopes that deliver clear, bright images even in low light conditions. Your waterproof, shockproof Burris scope will be covered by their Forever Warranty, which covers products for any material or craftsmanship defects for life, even if you're not the original owner. Gather information to help you with your purchase by browsing our collection of articles about riflescopes and reading through honest reviews of Burris riflescopes written by other customers. Remember that OpticsPlanet.com orders over $49 receive free shipping! Hit your long range target with Burris Eliminator III scopes -- the most advanced riflescopes on the planet.














